content: Fantastic drawing. I haven't put pencil to paper for a few years I'm considering going back into it but it's a matter of motivation & time. Do you recommend any tools to make your drawings more realistic?,pic.twitter.com/gc7ltaJ89w
You are very talented, it looks amazing
Would love to see Marco Reus pencil drawing
Love that you didn't hide the scar from the lobotomy he received for joining Arsenal.
Look at those details, am blown
Cool drawing, something seems off around the nose/mouth though. I think it has a slight slant. great skin texture, the darks are surely too dark for pure graphite, charcoal?
Sorry, seen you already did (23.7.17).  Kind of shows a mysterious side to him.
Superb.  Please do Granit Xhaka next.
Wow.. You are very talented ,amazing work
